e. Determining Optimal Clusters

1. Elbow method

fviz_nbclust(data,kmeans ,method = 'wss' )

# from here we can see that optimal no of cluster is 2

2. Silhouette method

fviz_nbclust(data,kmeans ,method = 'silhouette' )

fviz_nbclust(data,kmeans ,method = 'gap' )
